The help environment is simply a new tab for the [[AdvancedSearch|$:/AdvancedSearch]] function.

The help search simply searches for Shadow Tiddlers tagged with ''$:/HELP''. For your own plugins to utilize this, I recommend to package help tiddlers as shadow tiddlers in the path ``$:/help/<yourname>/<helptopic>``.
